# Code Generation Checklist

✓ Accesstrade only

✓ Campaign ID configurable

✓ Sub1 contains UserId

✓ URL validation exists

✓ AffiliateLink persisted

✓ Provider abstraction used

✓ No hardcoded cashback rates

✓ No direct HttpClient calls

✓ Authenticated user enforced

✓ Tracking supported

Affiliate tracking accuracy is more important than implementation speed.
